CHAT.comment: Language of Caregivers Mother South Shore , Massachusetts (has an r+less dialect; dialect overall similar to RI) Father Semi+Standard American English (originally from Rutland , Massachusetts located in center of the state) , sometimes shows evidence of an r+less dialect; vowel quality is generally like that of SAE.

CHI remains quiet , looks at MOT , then back at book
CHI plays with some sort of bubble wrapping she found
CHI continues to play with bubble wrapping
CHI turns the pages of the book .
CHI places bubble wrapping inside book
MOT brings CHI a velcro game to play , sits back down with CHI
MOT shows CHI how to play the game
CHI picks up and plays with game pieces
CHI still plays with game pieces , looks back at MOT
MOT is handed the laundry basket
MOT begins folding a towel , CHI reaches over and tugs at towel
CHI plays with folded towel , puts it aside , and sneezes
CHI picks up towel again , plays with it some more on her lap
CHI pulls at towel on her lap
CHI grabs at another towel from the laundry , places it on her lap
CHI continues to play with pieces from the game
CHI picks up game , plays with a piece some more
CHI tries to pry apart a piece of the game

CHI pulls away another piece from the game , looks at it
CHI hands the gamepiece to MOT
MOT kisses the gamepiece , then CHI imitates her and also kisses it
MOT pulls away the game to reveal all the pieces , CHI picks them up
MOT starts picking things up from the floor , CHI continues to play

CHI pushes teddy bear back into MOT's hands

one of the velcro gamepieces got stuck to CHI , MOT pulls it off

everybody is off camera , cannot tell what they are doing

camera is moved to CHI's room

CHI walks to dresser and opens a drawer
CHI sits down , continues to play with a pair of pants
CHI falls down , starts crying a little
CHI and MOT are back on camera , CHI sits down in her room
CHI gets up , picks up a diaper and walks over to MOT
MOT points to drawings on the diaper
MOT prepares to change CHI's diaper
CHI starts grabbing her backpack as her diaper is changed
CHI sits up , starts playing with her backpack
